                        "id": "18099099889913451",
                        "text": "Cheapest Michelin Lunch in Ginza, Tokyo \ud83c\udde8\ud83c\uddf3\u2728\n\n\ud83d\udccd Location: Canton 8 (Ginza) / \u559c\u7cb58\u53f7 8F, 8-2-1 Ginza, Chuo City, Tokyo A short walk from Ginza Station / Shimbashi Station \n\n\ud83d\udd52 Hours: 11:30 AM \u2013 3:00 PM, 5:30 PM \u2013 10:00 PM \n\ud83d\udcb0 Price: Lunch Sets from \u00a51,500\u20132,500 (Under $15)\n\nDid you know the world's cheapest Michelin 2-star restaurant is right here in Ginza? \ud83d\ude33\n\nThis place brings the legendary flavors of the Shanghai 2-star restaurant to Tokyo. We ordered the Shrimp Chili Lunch Set for under $15! The shrimps are massive, bouncy, and the sauce is absolutely refined. It\u2019s a hidden gem where you can enjoy luxury dining without breaking the bank!\n\nComment \"Michelin\" for more info \ud83d\udce9 \n\n#tokyo #ginza #canton8 #michelinstar #japanesefood #tokyofood #japantrip #localgem #gappyjapan"
                    }
                }
            ]
